nodes.title: Info
widgets_values:
================================
 JPS All in One Workflow - v6.0
================================

4 Generation Modes (blue nodes)
===============================

- TXT2IMG
- IMG2IMG
- Canny Control Net
- Depth Control Net

Strength and Ctrl-Options are not used by TXT2IMG.
Ctrl-Options are not uses by IMG2IMG.

Revision Mode (yellow nodes, left column)
=========================================

- ON/OFF Switch for Revision Mode
- Option to turn ON/OFF Positive/Negative TXT Prompts

All Options are only active if Revision Mode is turned ON. 

Image Adapter Mode (yellow nodes, right column)
===============================================

- ON/OFF Switch

You can use up to 3 pictures for input, but usually you get better results with 1 or 2.

Options are only active if the corresponding Image Adapter Mode is turned ON.

Additional Features
===================

- 4 image variants per generation - 0-30% SDXL Refiner
- history view
- clean layout with pipelines


Additional Info
===============

All required nodes should be available through ComfyUI Manager.

It's recommended to change "Link Render Mode" to "Straight" or "Hidden" for a better user experience, if you don't want to edit the workflow.

You have to change some nodes (base, refiner, VAE) to your own filenames, when you first use this workflow.

The option "base_percentage" is not used, as this workflow always generates 4 variants with 70-100% base percentage.
